-2,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to get product recommendations: rpc error: code = Unknown desc = Exception calling application: \\u003c_InactiveRpcError of RPC that terminated with:\\n\\tstatus = StatusCode.UNAVAILABLE\\n\\tdetails = \\\"\"failed to connect to all addresses\\\"\"\\n\\tdebug_error_string = \\\"\"{\\\"\"created\\\"\":\\\"\"@1749515297.165980692\\\"\",\\\"\"description\\\"\":\\\"\"Failed to pick subchannel\\\"\",\\\"\"file\\\"\":\\\"\"src/core/ext/filters/client_channel/client_channel.cc\\\"\",\\\"\"file_line\\\"\":3948,\\\"\"referenced_errors\\\"\":[{\\\"\"created\\\"\":\\\"\"@1749515297.165960119\\\"\",\\\"\"description\\\"\":\\\"\"failed to connect to all addresses\\\"\",\\\"\"file\\\"\":\\\"\"src/core/ext/filters/client_channel/lb_policy/pick_first/pick_first.cc\\\"\",\\\"\"file_line\\\"\":394,\\\"\"grpc_status\\\"\":14}]}\\\"\"\\n\\u003e\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"4bc3311f-7f86-4aee-ad53-77d19e5ac2af\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"GET\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"834d15b2-9cb8-4bcd-9695-0e58b070cf3e\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-10T00:28:17.182904851Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-07,frontend,frontend-1,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"could not retrieve currencies: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"6792c18f-c3c7-47ba-be0c-bea041b0a2cd\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"c30030db-67d7-452e-8362-bbf78bbfc423\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-10T00:30:25.83069568Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-07,frontend,frontend-1,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"could not retrieve currencies: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"ca045c55-efe3-41ac-8216-130297758059\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"834d15b2-9cb8-4bcd-9695-0e58b070cf3e\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-10T00:30:30.191046567Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-2", "frontend-1", "frontend-0", "recommendationservice-1"], "service_name": ["frontend", "recommendationservice"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-07", "aiops-k8s-03"]}, "matched_anomaly": "Determine the root cause of the system fault during 2025-06-10T00:10:28Z to 2025-06-10T00:35:28Z.", "time_range": "2025-06-10 00:10:28+00:00 to 2025-06-10 00:35:28+00:00"}, "trace_analysis_findings": "基于追踪数据分析，我已经收集到故障期间的详细调用链数据。现在需要其他智能体来收集日志和指标数据以进行完整的根因分析。\n\n根据追踪数据分析，我发现了以下关键问题：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"error_ratio\", \"frontend->recommendationservice\", \"recommendationservice->productcatalogservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"RecommendationService调用ProductCatalogService的延迟从正常2.92ms激增至519秒（延迟倍数177,000倍），出现超时错误状态码14\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\", \n      \"evidence\": \"前端服务出现大量HTTP 500错误和context canceled错误，影响推荐列表和产品目录查询功能\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现：**\n1. **严重的延迟问题**：RecommendationService调用ProductCatalogService的延迟从正常2.92ms激增至519秒，延迟增加超过17万倍\n2. **连接超时错误**：出现大量\"Connection timed out\"和\"failed to connect to all addresses\"错误\n3. **错误传播**：从RecommendationService的超时问题向上游传播到Frontend服务，导致前端返回HTTP 500错误\n\n**需要进一步调查：**\n- 需要日志智能体检查RecommendationService和ProductCatalogService的具体错误日志\n- 需要指标智能体分析相关服务的资源使用情况（CPU、内存、网络等）\n- 需要确认ProductCatalogService是否正常运行或存在资源瓶颈\n\n追踪数据显示这是一个典型的服务间依赖故障，RecommendationService无法正常访问ProductCatalogService是根因，导致整个调用链瘫痪。", "log_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的日志数据，我已经成功获取了故障期间的错误日志。现在让我分析这些日志数据来识别根因。\n\n从日志分析可以看出，故障期间存在明显的RPC连接问题。让我总结关键发现：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"context canceled\", \"failed to connect to all addresses\", \"StatusCode.UNAVAILABLE\", \"Connection timed out\", \"_InactiveRpcError\", \"Failed to pick subchannel\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"recommendationservice出现连接超时和无法连接到所有地址的问题，导致frontend服务的RPC调用失败\",\n      \"evidence\": \"recommendationservice-1日志显示：'failed to connect to all addresses', 'Connection timed out', 'grpc_status:14'\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend服务在调用recommendationservice时频繁出现context canceled错误，表明推荐服务不可用\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0/1/2日志显示：'failed to get product recommendations: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled'\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**分析总结**：\n\n1. **主要错误模式**：RPC连接失败，具体表现为：\n   - `context canceled` - 前端服务调用超时\n   - `failed to connect to all addresses` - 无法连接到推荐服务\n   - `Connection timed out` - 连接超时\n\n2. **故障传播路径**：\n   - recommendationservice出现连接问题（可能是网络问题或服务本身故障）\n   - frontend服务在调用recommendationservice时失败\n   - 故障影响到了产品推荐和购物车功能\n\n3. **关键证据**：\n   - recommendationservice-1的详细错误日志显示gRPC连接失败\n   - 三个frontend实例都报告了相同的错误模式\n   - 错误集中在00:11-00:28时间段，与故障时间窗口匹配\n\n这明显是一个服务间通信故障，recommendationservice是主要的嫌疑组件。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的指标数据，我已经完成了对系统故障的分析。以下是详细的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"client_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"shippingservice 服务出现严重的 client_error_ratio 和 error_ratio 异常，所有实例的错误率从0%飙升到42.86%-60%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice-0: error_ratio从0.0%上升到60.0%；shippingservice-1: error_ratio从0.0%上升到60.0%；shippingservice-2: error_ratio从0.0%上升到42.86%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend 服务出现显著的 rrt 和 rrt_max 延迟异常，同时伴随 server_error_ratio 增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0: rrt从12268.75ms上升到4867649.14ms(增长397倍)，rrt_max从241361ms上升到60001500ms；frontend-1: rrt从12429.36ms上升到8574981.57ms(增长689倍)；frontend-2: rrt从12598.31ms上升到9002837.95ms(增长714倍)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"recommendationservice-1 实例出现极端的 rrt 和 rrt_max 延迟异常，响应时间大幅增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt从3902.74ms上升到6725340.28ms(增长1722倍)，rrt_max从12499ms上升到39660312.36ms(增长3172倍)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析总结\n\n**主要发现**：\n1. **严重服务错误**：shippingservice 服务出现大规模故障，所有实例的错误率急剧上升\n2. **前端服务延迟爆炸**：frontend 服务响应时间增长数百倍，表明存在严重的性能瓶颈\n3. **推荐服务单实例异常**：recommendationservice-1 实例响应时间异常增长超过3000倍\n\n**故障模式识别**：\n- 这看起来是一个典型的级联故障，可能由 shippingservice 的故障引发，导致依赖它的 frontend 服务延迟增加\n- recommendationservice-1 的单实例异常可能表明该实例存在资源瓶颈或配置问题\n\n**建议后续调查方向**：\n- 检查 shippingservice 的日志以确定具体的错误原因\n- 分析 recommendationservice-1 所在节点的资源使用情况\n- 查看 frontend 与 shippingservice 之间的调用链路关系"}
